video_title: Ask yourself: "What can I learn from this?" #inspiration #positivity #podcast
transcript:
you don't have to love a job to learn
from it and I think we all are thinking
well I hate my job I dislike it it's the
worst it's a waste of time I'm in the
wrong place but actually if you just
shift that to be like what can I learn
what experience do I not have how can I
interact how do I not want to behave
like this boss drives me crazy I'll
never be this boss I remember I had a
boss
